  "prompt": "How do I log in my Facebook account if you forgot your password?",
  "response": "To recover your Facebook account if you've forgotten your password, follow these steps:\n\n1. Go to the Facebook login page\n\n2. Click on \"Forgotten password?\"\n\n3. You can then recover your password in several ways:\n- Enter your email address or phone number\n- Search for your account\n- Use a different method like sending a code to your email or phone\n\n4. Choose a recovery method:\n- Get a code via email\n- Get a code via text message\n- Use a trusted contact\n- Identify your friends in photos\n\n5. Enter the recovery code you receive\n\n6. Create a new password\n\n7. Log in with your new password\n\nTips:\n- Make sure you're on the official Facebook website\n- Check your spam folder if you don't receive the code\n- Use a strong, unique password\n- Consider using a password manager\n\nIf you continue to have trouble, contact Facebook support directly.",
